{"tid":1690381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋有星火612 點解唔可以有主動告黑警嘅基金？","createTime":"2019-11-03T09:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T12:54:40.000Z","uid":78449,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5e2cae2e66bcbd2b53f1c02d0e4182a2b58563","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">星火</span> 對於係革命中被捕嘅手足真係好有用<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">612</span> 雖然難批 但至少都有佢幫助到嘅地方<br />\n以上嘅基金/組織（以下合稱組織）都係手足們嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">盾</span></span><br />\n但！點解我哋唔可以有比我哋嘅主動去告班狗嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">矛</span></span>？<br />\n我哋可以有一個基金/組織 比受害者提供要告們狗嘅意見or資金（要告必須原告在埋） 而家啲狗唔會告返自己狗 要告只可以靠我哋搵律師<br />\n一定有好多無辜嘅同路人或手足被無理甚至暴力對待，唔知可唔可行？ 定已經有相關嘅組織 可唔可以發大嚟搞？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 無相關知識"},{"pid":"891446a0ed2f12ab99d5f01a4f90672ad31a9217","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e3a0a9f04660a8bf78917b84842ce3ffbacc287","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"推 求解答"},{"pid":"803260ff0ac5b62c81f6213bfc584553cd1913fe","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"推 求解答"},{"pid":"7ceeb643845acbf20e68d94545db36d5267b2777","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"推 求解答"},{"pid":"1cecd6af02cb8831a9bdf62e88e18f76cf9bb190","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"推 求解答"},{"pid":"e20ec7f657d36d2a439e08bbf6bdb23e8e13f1ed","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"推 求解答"},{"pid":"92536ef11c59d351e89c307ed8c9f29e20f86054","tid":1690381,"uid":78449,"like":0,"disli